title: Days of our Lives S52E213 Friday, July 21, 2017
description:
Abigail and Chad's deep feelings for each other resurface.





Hope, Lani, and Eli close in on Dario.





A protective JJ runs into Chad and warns him not to cause his sister any further pain.





Hope reluctantly tells Rafe the truth about Dario.





Anjelica ropes another face from Salem's past into her master plan
